data.title: Compelled (Short 2022)
data.meta_description: Compelled: Directed by Estelle Martre, Julien Martre. With Sarah Foulkes, Julien Martre. Alice awaits her brother Jake's arrival at their newly purchased house, but receives a FaceTime call from him explaining that he won't be able to make it tonight. Meanwhile, she discovers a creepy mask hidden in a hole in the floor, which appears to be connected to the unnerving events that follow.
